TITLE: Configuring Docker Compose for Permify with Postgres and Redis
DESCRIPTION: A Docker Compose configuration that sets up a complete Permify environment with three services: Permify authorization engine, PostgreSQL database, and Redis cache. Each service is configured with appropriate environment variables, ports, and dependencies.
SOURCE: https://github.com/Permify/permify/blob/master/docs/docs/api-overview/reference/snap-tokens.md#2025-04-17_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: yaml
